ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/11167/documentation

This datasets represents construction of average dairy wich have production facilities to produce different dairy products, such as milk, cheese and butter.

Includes the building and the equipment (cooling and heating equipment, tanks, storage room).
